name: Planet Earth Men's Insulated Pant
description: These pants are beige or a greenish tan color. They are made by "Planet Earth" and are a size MEDIUM. They are insulated snow pants. They have cargo pockets, and zippers on the bottom for your boots. They also have a few zippers for storing things. These pants are great. Only wore them one time. They are VERY similar to the "outpost" style Planet Earth currently sells but they are not identical, as they have been sitting in the garage for a few seasons. They are called the Planet Earth "Drop" Pant..They are in NEW condition, minus the tags. (The picture is really terrible, google the outpost style and you'll get the idea)

name: Betsey Johnson Asian Jungle Tiger Earrings
description: Betsey Johnson Asian Jungle Tiger Earrings never worn. Originally $30. No longer sold in stores. Can't find on amazon, only on ebay @ $21 or more. Earrings only, threw away the tag. Used stock photo. Hope you like it :)

name: Juicy Couture Gigi Black Fairytale Purse
description: I am selling my 100% authentic Juicy Couture purse. The style name is "Gigi Fairytale" and it is a black velour bag, with white/ivory stitching, a black/white/ivory satin bow, one outside side pocket, a "pleather" J inside of a heart stitched onto the back, a medal chained medallion that says Royal Juicy on it, and has a small pleather heart attached, a pleather zipper pull with a medal accessory that has the juicy couture scottie dog printed on it. Inside fabric is tan with crowns and "Love" written on it, a silver cell phone pocket with "Hello?" written on it, a silver zip pocket that says SHOP! on it and has a J zipper pull. Authentic Juicy Couture tag on inside. I have the receipt, it's a little bit faded but you can still read it. I payed $134 for the bag, but thanks to our economy it's only worth 1/3 of the price :( otherwise listed on ebay for $55 usually. Stock photo posted. No dust bag was included at time of purchase. Hope you like it :)

name: Bob Siemons Symbols of Faith Charm Bracelet
description: Symbols of faith charm bracelet by Bob Siemon Designs. Originally $27.99. Rhodium plated sterling silver, lifetime guarantee, lightly worn, but in good condition. Charms are: a heart with a cross inside, a butterfly, a christian fish symbol, a bible, a cross, an angel, a dove, a key that says "Jesus" on it, an anchor, and a lamb. Bracelet comes in original box. I used a stock photo. Hope you like it :)

name: Emily Strange Patchwork Plush Sabbath
description: I am selling my beloved patchwork sabbath plush by Emily Strange. It is in good condition, lightly loved, but no holes, smells, rips, tears, etc. It has no tags other than the tush tag. This item is from the 2002 collection, and is quite difficult to find. The only one on ebay at the moment is $78.95. It would make a perfect gift for any Emily fan! I used my own photo, but you can also google photos to see what it looks like in more detail! Hope you like it :)
